<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="all-right-int">all right <strong><em>int</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɔːl 'raɪt/    美 /ɔːl 'raɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>好了：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>All right, now I’d like to introduce the first speaker.
好了，现在我来介绍第一位发言人。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>— Are you sure you won’t come for a drink with us?
— <strong><em>_</em></strong>, if you insist.  （2013 全国）<br />
A.Not at all<br />
B.It depends<br />
C.All right then<br />
D.I don’t care  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. C  </p></div>